OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPlayStation to axe 900 jobs
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fand close London studio    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sony has announced it will lay off 8%  
OL,6, of PlayStation employees globally,     
OL,7, amounting to approximately 900 people. 
OL,9,FIn addition to cuts in the US and      
OL,10,FJapan, the gaming giant said this would
OL,11,Fmean closing PlayStation's London      
OL,12,FStudio entirely.                       
OL,14,FIn a blog post sharing an email sent to
OL,15,Femployees, boss Jim Ryan called the    
OL,16,Fmove "sad news" and said it was "a     
OL,17,Fdifficult day at our company".         
OL,19,F"We have concluded that tough decisions
OL,20,Fhave become inevitable," he said.      
